The mother of a British woman shot dead 
on holiday in Turkey has denied claims her daughter was 
having an affair with the man accused of shooting her.

Cecilia Bury, 87, shook her head and said she was not aware Anne, 56, was having an affair with gardener Veli Acar.

The accusations emerged in the aftermath of the barbaric shooting with locals suggesting he had
flown into a jealous rage after seeing Anne with another man.

