Speaking from the Tiryaki Boutique Hotel in Fethiye her brothers said: 'It is completely untrue.'

Cecilia, who was also shot in Monday's savage attack, shook her head, frowned and added: 'No that's not true.'

She was released from hospital on Tuesday was recuperating from her injuries at the boutique hotel, while her two sons made arrangements to repatriate their sister's body to the UK.

In a statement today, Miss Bury's family said they 'cannot comprehend the mentality' of the gunman who killed her and injured her mother Cecilia and son Alex.

